About Elemento :: Parent

Elemento brings HTML templates and other goodies to GWT Elemental

Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
Elemento :: Core Core classes
Elemento :: GIN Annotation processor which generated GIN providers for injectable HTML templates
Elemento :: Template Annotation processor to bind elements to HTML templates
